items.name: Matchbox Cars Wiki
items.title: Matchbox Cars Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to Matchbox Cars Wiki!
items.desc:
The goal of the Matchbox Wiki is to create the most comprehensive source of Matchbox toys on the Internet. It was started in October 2008 by Kevin Harbin.

We provide the best resource for tracking and cataloguing the different cars available, from ambulances to Volkswagons. We have models, makes, and all the specifications for the entire history of Matchbox cars.

items.name: Pixar Cars Wiki
items.title: Pixar Cars Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Pixar Cars Wiki!
items.desc:
The wiki about Disney-Pixar's Cars the movies and short films that anyone can edit!

In "Cars", Lightning McQueen ends up in a small town off the edge of Route 66. Though originally wanting to go back home, he later warms up to the town and decides to stay until his race against The King and Chick Hicks.

"Cars 2" sees Mater becomes a secret agent and goes around the world to stop the evil plans of Miles Axlerod and Professor Z, backed up by Lightning's racing challenge from famous race car Francesco Bernoulli.

items.name: World of Cars Online Wiki
items.title: World of Cars Online Wiki
items.headline: Learn more about the World Of Cars Online Wiki!
items.desc: The World Of Cars Online, a fun online Disney Cars game! Made by Pixar, this fun game, (now closed) is fun, although the game is closed, the game is still very fun! You can choose your own character type, car type, name, color, and number! In this wiki you will learn so much about The World of Cars Online, that you will fall in love with it! We also offer high-quality images and character pages, so that you can learn all of the characters! This game allows you to chat with other people online! You can drive around town by Flo's V8 Cafe, and other famous Radiator Springs Places!

items.name: World of Cars Wiki
items.title: World of Cars Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to World of Cars
items.desc: Cars is a CGI animated film series and Disney media franchise that began with the 2006 film, Cars, produced by Pixar and distributed by Walt Disney Pictures. The film was followed by a sequel in 2011, two spin-off film, Planes and Planes: Fire and Rescue, produced by DisneyToon Studios in 2013 and 2014, and another sequel in 2017. The first two films were directed by John Lasseter, the CEO of Pixar Animation Studios. Cars is considered to be Pixar's "anniversary" franchise as the first two films marked Pixar's 20th and 25th anniversaries respectively.[according to whom?] Together, the three films have accrued over $1 billion in box office revenue worldwide.

items.headline: Learn more about the world of classic cars!
items.desc:
The Classic Car Wiki focuses on all cars from around the globe which are over 25 years of age which including buses, vans and military vehicles. We also focus on famous cars from TV and Movies. We have information and photos of all your favourite cars including the Jaguar E-Type, Ford Mustang and Chevrolet Bel Air. 

We have recently been adding pages on racecars, military vehicles and concept cars.

Why not come and discover the world's best classic cars?

items.name: Projectcars Wiki
items.title: Projectcars Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Project Cars Wiki!
items.desc: Project CARS features world-class graphics and handling, a ground-breaking dynamic time of day & weather system, and deep tuning & pit stop functionality. It also features four modes, represented by the stripes in the logo: Career, Solo, Online and Community. With a huge range of cars and motorsports, there is something perfect for everyone who likes to drive fast. Create your driver, pick your motorsport and shift into high gear. This wikia is in need of contributors who are fans of the game and would like to join our community. Come visit us in the chat room or talk with us in the forums!
